OL,4,C'extremely poor' refereeing in Everton
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FForest say they are "considering their
OL,8,Foptions" over "extremely poor"
OL,9,Frefereeing decisions, following their
OL,10,F2-0 defeat at Everton on the weekend.
OL,12,FThe club posted the statement on
OL,13,Fsocial media after yesterday's match
OL,14,Fat Goodison Park left them one point
OL,15,Fabove the relegation zone.
OL,17,FDuring the match Forest were denied
OL,18,Fthree penalty decisions after VAR
OL,19,Freviewed the incidents.
